Device A ip - > 192.168.1.10
Device B ip - > 192.168.1.11
Network -> 192.168.1.0

Switch : Create a connect to connect A and B devices 

Switch command: 
    - > ip link ( To connect network)
    - > ip addr add  
    
Router :  A Router helps connect two networks together. It is an intelligent device. conencts two seperate network
To see routing configuration :
      -> route 
      ->  ip route add 
  
